1098
01:05:48,158 --> 01:05:50,727
我很害怕会失去你
I was so scared that I'd loose you, you see?

1099
01:05:51,025 --> 01:05:52,910
我真的希望事情不是这个样子的
And I wish it weren't like this, I...

