I wish we could go back to the beginning and start this dance again.

1101
01:05:55,748 --> 01:05:57,969
我,自行车,还有你
Me and the bicycle and you,

1102
01:05:57,969 --> 01:05:59,999
你是那么美丽,当我看着你的时候简直觉得疼
So beautiful that it hurts to look at you.

1103
01:06:02,362 --> 01:06:06,252
求你,不管你将要听到什么,请你相信我
Please, whatever you're about to hear, please, please believe me.

