What are you doing?

1166
01:11:01,625 --> 01:11:02,505
放开他!
Get off him!

1167
01:11:05,565 --> 01:11:06,723
你别动
You stay there.

1168
01:11:13,145 --> 01:11:14,383
弗吉尼亚
Virginia!

1169
01:11:17,828 --> 01:11:20,906
为我们干杯
A toast. To us.

1170
01:11:22,527 --> 01:11:26,595
